  "text": "Here we use a class of problems called the maximum of two quadratics (MTQ) that have been widely used to test the global optimization ability of CCEAs in [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] , and [CITATION_3] . These problems include a global optimum and a local suboptimum, where the suboptimum covers a much wider range of the search space and is thus difficult for conventional CCEAs to escape from.",
